    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>★ 关于体验版 ★</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－体验版可游玩至游戏中的第 5 天早上，约 1 ~ 2 小时的游戏时长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >－可遇到两名可追求的好感角色，进行对话、送礼、探险邀请</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P.S. 若要将体验版的存档移至正式版继续使用，可参考讨论区的置顶教学！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>★ 关于正式版 ★</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/29c04879afda86938d31c4b5e82dd2c3.avif?t=1765351752\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras_big/29c04879afda86938d31c4b5e82dd2c3.avif?t=1765351752 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款结合战斗与生活模拟的限时类轻养成游戏，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演实习中的炼金术士，为了向父母证明自己的能力，独自前往亚斯达小镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这 90 天内，你可以自由安排时间，去小镇上课、打工，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或是邀约伙伴，去镇外的探险地收集素材，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着时间的推移，你也可以前往附近的群岛，或是参与小镇内的节日活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总之，这 90 天，就是属于你的日子。  <br>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/caa43407f2ef32dca8f5122fc251de55.avif?t=1765351752\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras_big/caa43407f2ef32dca8f5122fc251de55.avif?t=1765351752 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  炼制药剂：为了赚取更多金钱和交货点数，认真炼制药剂吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/40eb7ddd21b852b8a9892527d627ac2a.avif?t=1765351752\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras_big/40eb7ddd21b852b8a9892527d627ac2a.avif?t=1765351752 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  战斗系统：加入【天气操控】及【状态平衡值 BP】，拥有更丰富的战斗策略！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/af1fc0f286995221cd079acdc649974e.poster.avif?t=1765351752\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/af1fc0f286995221cd079acdc649974e.webm?t=1765351752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/af1fc0f286995221cd079acdc649974e.mp4?t=1765351752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ 骑鸡泡澡：体力不够的时候，就跟鸡仔一起泡澡来恢复体力吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/7a0a2b80882fc3fda6b386f740d840bf.poster.avif?t=1765351752\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/7a0a2b80882fc3fda6b386f740d840bf.webm?t=1765351752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/7a0a2b80882fc3fda6b386f740d840bf.mp4?t=1765351752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  好感角色：想更进一步了解他们吗？可以透过对话、送礼，以及邀请探险来有更多互动！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras/43427b4baedba28530b1ce0559dc5bd6.avif?t=1765351752\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070650/extras_big/43427b4baedba28530b1ce0559dc5bd6.avif?t=1765351752 width=800 height=271 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p>",
